14	Startup Party #6	startup-party-6	<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;" id="docs-internal-guid-fd1985bc-0db0-1ff0-fb63-f49905ce776b"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">The next Startup Party will happen on the Friday 10th of February at Emerald Hub, will begin  at 6pm and it is now time to prepare it all together since you are invited!</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">A Startup Party is a time for all the startup community in Phnom Penh, and each startup, entrepreneur, investor, student is invited to join. The purpose of the event is to share business ideas, ambitions but also experiences and projects.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">The event is about gathering together people that share the same view and want to be a part of the growing startup community.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">The Startup Party is an event where you can learn more about what is going on in the startup world in the capital. In order to do so, every startup, everyone who wants  to speak to present an idea or a business will be invited to do so. One minute, a few questions and laughs will be enough to make you be a member of this friendly community. </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">The point is to generate a dynamical community where every project is known and where we can all support each other projects.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">A few startups will be invited to pitch. It will be interesting for the audience to learn more about some businesses that are developing in town and after a 5min presentation, it will be possible to ask questions.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">Pitching a business is a real challenge and it is important to practice it, that’s why we offer the opportunity for a few startups to come and stand out in front of the community to make their projects more known.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">The event is however about having fun and sharing so networking, snacks, drinks and games will be organized to bring the community together.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">We hope to see you there!</span></p>     \r\n            	2017-02-10 17:30:00		0	7	2017-02-05 16:52:54.13611
